title: The One with Monica's Thunder
synopsis: Monica excitedly reveals the good news of her engagement to everyone -- but Rachel and Ross upstage her by reuniting.

title: The One with Rachel's Book
synopsis: Joey finds out that Rachel is reading a steamy romance novel. Monica discovers that her parents have spent the money for her wedding on a beach house.

title: The One with Phoebe's Cookies
synopsis: Monica becomes obsessed with acquiring Phoebe's secret, delicious cookie recipe. Joey accepts Rachel's help with sailing.

title: The One with Rachel's Assistant
synopsis: Rachel wants to hire a cute, young male assistant over a more qualified woman. Joey's show gets cancelled.

title: The One with the Engagement Picture
synopsis: Joey tries to teach Chandler how to smile for an engagement picture with Monica. Joey takes Tag out for a good time.

title: The One with the Nap Partners
synopsis: Rachel and Phoebe compete to be Monica's maid of honor -- but Monica doesn't want to make the decision.

title: The One with Ross' Library Book
synopsis: Ross discovers that his dissertation is in a section of the library where students go to have sex. Rachel and Phoebe meddle in Joey's relationship.

title: The One Where Chandler Doesn't Like Dogs
synopsis: Chandler's irrational fear of dogs causes problems when Phoebe brings home a cute canine. Rachel's assistant gives her a Thanksgiving surprise.

title: The One with All the Candy
synopsis: Monica becomes popular with her neighbors because of her homemade candy. Phoebe decides to learn to ride a bicycle.

title: The One with the Holiday Armadillo
synopsis: Ross dresses up as the Holiday Armadillo and, with Monica, Chandler and Joey's help, teaches Ben about Chanukah.

title: The One with All the Cheesecakes
synopsis: Chandler and Rachel can't help eating the irresistible cheesecakes intended for a neighbor. Phoebe's former boyfriend returns for one night only.

title: The One Where They're Up All Night
synopsis: Monica falls asleep during sex. Rachel argues with Tag. Ross and Joey get stranded on the roof.

title: The One Where Rosita Dies
synopsis: Phoebe becomes involved with a suicidal office worker. Rachel breaks Joey's favorite chair. Monica's beloved childhood belongings are destroyed.

title: The One Where They All Turn Thirty
synopsis: Rachel's 30th birthday prompts the friends to reminisce about their own 30th birthdays.

title: The One with Joey's New Brain
synopsis: Joey's character on a daytime drama becomes more prominent -- to the chagrin of the show's diva star.

title: The One with the Truth About London
synopsis: Chandler finds out who Monica really wanted to have sex with on the night they became lovers. Ross is mad after Rachel teaches Ben practical jokes.

title: The One with the Cheap Wedding Dress
synopsis: Monica battles another shopper for the perfect wedding dress. Ross and Joey compete for the same woman.

title: The One with Joey's Award
synopsis: Joey overreacts at a daytime drama awards show. Ross deals with a male student who says he's in love with him.

title: The One with Ross and Monica's Cousin
synopsis: Monica's gorgeous cousin unwittingly wreaks havoc on Chandler and Ross. Rachel and Phoebe hastily plan a surprise bridal party for Monica.

title: The One with Rachel's Big Kiss
synopsis: Rachel reveals a titillating secret about her and a former sorority sister. Ross and Chandler compete for wedding tuxedos.

title: The One with the Vows
synopsis: As Monica and Chandler prepare their wedding vows, everyone reminisces.

title: The One with Chandler's Dad
synopsis: Chandler confronts his estranged, cross-dressing father. Rachel gets into trouble driving Monica's Porsche.

title: The One with Chandler and Monica's Wedding: Part 1
synopsis: As the relatives gather for Monica and Chandler's wedding, Chandler finally realizes the magnitude of what he's doing.

title: The One with Chandler and Monica's Wedding: Part 2
synopsis: Monica remains blissfully unaware of the potential disasters on her wedding day.
